====Sell Price &amp; Quality====
A number of points for each item are awarded based on its sell price and quality, with a maximum of 8 points per item. The sell price used in-game is the actual sell price, not the base sell price. For example, a gold-quality item with a base sell price of {{Price|200}} would earn points for having an actual sell price of {{Price|300}} '''and''' for being gold quality. Note that this means that [[Options#Advanced Game Options|Profit Margins]] selected on the creation of the farm in Advanced Game Options affects the point value.

